The Python error says that it cannot find the Cantera package. Check to 
see that there is a folder called &quot;Cantera&quot; in 
C:&#92;Python24&#92;Lib&#92;site-packages. If there is not, then you need to run 
the installer for the Cantera Python package 
(Cantera-1.5.5.win32-py2.4.exe) that should be in C:&#92;Cantera.

As far as the C++ errors, these seem to be some configuration problem 
with missing files in your debugger, not a Cantera problem...

